# DECODER is an integrated framework which performs de novo deconvolution, and compartment weight estimation for a single sample.
# Peng et. al.

# For de novo deconvolution, ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# simplely call the function as below:

Decon_de_novo(configFile)

# "configFile" is a configuration file that provides input files and parameters, a demo of which is config_de_novo.tsv.
# The user needs to prepare a data matrix file with format .mat, .tsv or .csv.

# For single-sample deconvolution,----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# simplely call the function as below:

Decon_single_sample(configFile)

# "configFile" is a configuration file that provides input files and parameters, a demo of which is config_de_novo.tsv.
# The user needs to prepare a data matrix file with format .mat, .tsv or .csv.
# A reference dataset needs to be determined. Options are TCGA cancer types, e.g. TCGA_RNAseq_PAAD.
